Add JSON metrics for T-HEAD Yitian 710 SoC DDR.

Reviewed-by: John Garry <john.g.garry@oracle.com>
Signed-off-by: Jing Zhang <renyu.zj@linux.alibaba.com>
Acked-by: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
